Summary:        Fast lossless compression algorithm
Name:           zstd
Version:        1.5.2
Release:        2%{?dist}
License:        BSD and GPLv2
URL:            https://github.com/facebook/zstd
Group:          Applications/System
Vendor:         VMware, Inc.
Distribution:   Photon

Source0: https://github.com/facebook/zstd/archive/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
